<node id="A部門">
  <data key="d0">A部門</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">A部門 is an organizational unit within B客戶's company that handles various maintenance tasks. This department is involved in specific activities during maintenance, such as account inventory checks and other routine maintenance duties. A部門 plays a crucial role in performing maintenance activities related to Splunk role capabilities and generating monthly reports. Additionally, the department has been involved in user permission adjustments concerning Splunk, including IP address adjustments, software upgrades, and NTP service checks among others. This department is part of the broader organizational structure responsible for ensuring the smooth operation and upkeep of systems within B客戶's organization.&lt;SEP&gt;#a部门is a department involved in several of the daily maintenance tasks listed for B客户.&lt;SEP&gt;A部門is involved in confirming the maintainer's account permissions and conducting health checks for systems.&lt;SEP&gt;A department involved in the maintenance process.&lt;SEP&gt;A部門is a department within the organization where B客户的维护工作发生。</data>
