<node id="B部門">
  <data key="d0">B部門</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">B部門 is a department within B客戶's organization that is involved in various maintenance tasks and activities. This includes managing API access requests, conducting KVstore engine tests, performing data containment for FISAC (a system or project), and undertaking additional maintenance activities such as system testing. Additionally, B部門 is responsible for setting up FIsec intelligence retrieval configurations and adding indexers to the IDX cluster nodes. The department plays a crucial role in ensuring that the organization's systems are operational and functioning correctly by handling tasks related to data collection, system testing, and other necessary maintenance procedures.</data>
