<node id="E客戶">
  <data key="d0">E客戶</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">E客户 is a client company or organization for which detailed maintenance records are maintained. The entity undergoes various types of maintenance work, including specific instances such as maintenance conducted by Splunk in October 2025. Maintenance activities and the documentation thereof are central to E客户的 relationship with service providers, ensuring that all interactions and services provided to E客户 are accurately recorded and tracked over time. This includes maintaining records for Splunk systems and other related services, emphasizing the importance of detailed documentation in their ongoing maintenance processes.&lt;SEP&gt;E客戶is a client company for which maintenance records are kept.&lt;SEP&gt;E客戶is a client for whom maintenance work was conducted.&lt;SEP&gt;E客戶is a client for whom maintenance work was performed by an engineer.&lt;SEP&gt;E客戶is a customer whose maintenance records are being documented.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-1e6839b81653aa7c9b7ec794f3447380&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fcc4bf66788ce00c23c3e736753ea50a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3c4967b23b72f04d5c4ef37149d21ede&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-738a58105cbf665748b3257e0cfee9ac&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8a40e782f3c3804da0a1d45dfa05eefe&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8bddb98b4a84e394c0a4558b42ae12d0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1df6d8d113790f99d50593095e1e5e58&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c0c6684aa00106f16e7869f519061642&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5096c0cdf6972a3670732e4f9be1d36a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d02e98febcd8f8650bbe77d789a41d69&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b6f1e5469f6278ea8a34bff96b293b69&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-996c8aba3ce4de0e9bb90c0d569231f3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b0add79f46581b83deba682a2c89cdb7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0640212d45b4b92d91d0255cf90edf96&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c0cd3e323fc2a43e461d7af757b08706&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-25d7c29d65aa0e4d54fb4af54207fa0d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d0cef05272158ef916c2b84f625b2ddb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-76068a2f95fd89e7ceb4741d4eb478ce&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cafeb58d25cc4cbc85eaf07cf415496a</data>
