487592cef5210f2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-25d7c29d65aa0e4d54fb4af54207fa0d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d0cef05272158ef916c2b84f625b2ddb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-203eba714089c79438cfc39755f054ce&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-76068a2f95fd89e7ceb4741d4eb478ce&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-15d6c505e6a20b598aa21d52b466adcd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2fe3f974e54dd1f1ad98289cc79980d6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-41be59e9bae9e87a716afd8b5a9e9ee1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cf168eec40aae386455af5027929f6fe&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4861ed7c0c566a81f361adb6811a1523&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-17b29d261b8bce3ef9105d1c8a78415d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f6caccf00501b5f4caf06dcfc047ae9e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-04465635a6b88183cbabbfe7e25635dd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0d3d3acb3c191c9e65fac21b5ed9284f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d96ca3133c54d9d76add7de434ee05b5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3f8775862e3b8ea072578967e7520445&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cafeb58d25cc4cbc85eaf07cf415496a</data>
  <data key="d2">The World Athletics Federation is an organization responsible for overseeing a wide range of activities within the realm of global athletics. It manages the rules and regulations that govern athletes participating in international championships, such as Noah Carter. The federation plays a crucial role in organizing and supervising major events like the World Athletics Championship, ensuring the smooth operation and high standards of these competitions. Additionally, it is responsible for validating athletic records to ensure accuracy and fairness across all global athletic competitions. This includes overseeing various athletics events and maintaining rigorous record validations to uphold integrity within the sport.&lt;SEP&gt;The World Athletics Federation oversees the World Athletics Championship and validates athletic records.</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773713548</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="C客戶">
  <data key="d0">C客戶</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">C客戶 is an entity representing an organization or company that receives maintenance services. This entity can be referred to as both a client and a customer in various contexts, with consistent acknowledgment across multiple descriptions. Maintenance records are documented and kept for C客戶, ensuring a detailed history of its service interactions and requirements. These records serve to maintain accurate and up-to-date information about the organization’s maintenance needs and activities. The documentation process involves recording all relevant maintenance activities performed on behalf of C客戶, thereby providing a comprehensive overview of past and current maintenance services conducted for this entity.&lt;SEP&gt;C客戶is the client for whom maintenance activities are recorded.&lt;SEP&gt;C客戶is the client for whom maintenance activities were recorded.&lt;SEP&gt;C客戶is the client for whom maintenance services were conducted.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-082efb5c18d778427dcd94905e5f4370&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cdd29ae3537f38a27c3848632ad51359&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1ff26e3a56f4aaf4bbd7c0dfae03685b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1e7cec156f57837e8d25cbe83a6db45f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7c1fca5402ff2eb1c53222e1d4db282a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0b9e37e8f7e8a98183b1724c16ce814a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-068ca517cbebf973fd4089bd45ef615c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ab226f704fc1b4d45dd06222f40cb39f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c41e50d3a458388dc7fe53ece68ee69f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-79f23819b8640c43571e6e9b3e4098e0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5479196dee25b34d077c01190c6c728b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5930b403906ecb929487592cef5210f2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-15d6c505e6a20b598aa21d52b466adcd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2fe3f974e54dd1f1ad98289cc79980d6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f6caccf00501b5f4caf06dcfc047ae9e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0d3d3acb3c191c9e65fac21b5ed9284f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b8ec2739edb4ee1ccc4cf68534e90be5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3f8775862e3b8ea072578967e7520445</data>
