  <data key="d8">(A人員, B客戶) describes a relationship where A人員 provides various maintenance and support services for B客戶. The primary responsibility of A人員 includes maintaining and supporting B客户的设备 (B客户's equipment). Specifically, A人员 performs tasks such as technical support and system maintenance to ensure the smooth operation of B客户的设施. These activities are recorded in B客戶的維護紀錄 (maintenance records) which document the services provided by A人員.

A人員 is involved in multiple aspects of maintenance work for B客户提供, including providing necessary services that keep B客户's systems running efficiently. The relationship between A人员 and B客户 emphasizes the importance of regular maintenance and timely support to meet B客户的 needs and requirements.&lt;SEP&gt;A人员负责为B客户处理维护记录，表明了服务和支持关系。&lt;SEP&gt;A personnel was responsible for conducting maintenance on B客户的systems.&lt;SEP&gt;A人員handles maintenance tasks related to B客戶's services.&lt;SEP&gt;A人員provided maintenance services for B客戶as documented in the record.&lt;SEP&gt;A人员is responsible for maintaining systems for B客户.</data>
  <data key="d9">client-engineer,engineer involvement,engineering support,maintenance,maintenance record,maintenance service,maintenance support,record keeping,responsibility,service,service provider,service provision,service support,support</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-daa296a353c26f41dfc613743d24e936&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-72f381579d364fa91cc3e73153e0af97&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-95280ea367581dac710f0dc56c7a72f3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0944d4a59fb7a84bd79d2fca8361e518&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-75fa98905e1d68515f390e75c46adddb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3781d1671ca7126e99e7656264965fb6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f62a98ad02d11a4c9618cbda43281859&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e2a0171ee9d19cc664d4d041d3e73ba2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-333af5cc1ff286e512f36be66d1aa78b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fe7268a7cb94439d483759e501068db6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cf168eec40aae386455af5027929f6fe&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-04465635a6b88183cbabbfe7e25635dd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d96ca3133c54d9d76add7de434ee05b5</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
