  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="B客戶" target="C人員">
  <data key="d7">14.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The relationship between (B客户, C人员) involves the provision of maintenance and support services by C人员 to B客户. This includes various types of technical assistance such as addressing issues with the Splunk indexer queue and handling problems related to IDX hard drive space and data synchronization. Additionally, C人员 maintains a record of these interactions and provides ongoing support services for B客户的 system maintenance needs.

C人员 consistently engages in activities that ensure the smooth operation and upkeep of B客户's systems, including regular service check-ins and issue resolution. This relationship underscores the importance of continuous communication and collaboration between B客户 and C人员 to address any technical challenges efficiently.&lt;SEP&gt;C人員参与了对B客户的维护工作。&lt;SEP&gt;C人员also provides maintenance services for B客户.&lt;SEP&gt;B客户也需要C人员参与其系统的维护工作。&lt;SEP&gt;C人员同样参与对B客户的系统维护工作，体现维护和服务支持的关系。&lt;SEP&gt;C人員is also responsible for maintaining B客戶's services.&lt;SEP&gt;C人员also provides maintenance services for B客户.</data>
  <data key="d9">client-engineer,engineer involvement,engineering support,maintenance,maintenance client,maintenance service,maintenance support,maintenance work,record keeping,responsibility,service,service provider,service provision,service support,support</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-daa296a353c26f41dfc613743d24e936&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-72f381579d364fa91cc3e73153e0af97&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-412e17859c430b9ce8b929bc152053ef&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-39206ec5906f23d68e051b1df74d3ca7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-95280ea367581dac710f0dc56c7a72f3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d0d3b88d3601a1081c8354e0ef27952f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1e6e1908b68b82814f06780675f7938b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-84c3e0271089b72556be831ea38a055f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0944d4a59fb7a84bd79d2fca8361e518&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3781d1671ca7126e99e7656264965fb6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f62a98ad02d11a4c9618cbda43281859&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-333af5cc1ff286e512f36be66d1aa78b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cf168eec40aae386455af5027929f6fe&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d96ca3133c54d9d76add7de434ee05b5</data>
