<edge source="Noah Carter" target="World Athletics Federation">
  <data key="d7">40.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The World Athletics Federation is responsible for overseeing rules, regulations, and standards governing athletes such as Noah Carter when they compete in international championships. This organization plays a crucial role in validating records set by these athletes, including Noah Carter's record-breaking performance where his new 100m sprint record was officially recorded and recognized. The World Athletics Federation ensures compliance with established norms and guidelines, validates both performance results and equipment use by athletes, and monitors their participation in events according to set rules and guidelines.

The federation sets standards for athletic achievements and maintains the integrity of the sport by overseeing record validations and competition rules. It validates new records set by athletes like Noah Carter and oversees the championship where these records are established. The World Athletics Federation ensures that all rules and regulations under which athletes compete, such as those related to Noah Carter's participation in championships, are strictly followed. This includes overseeing athletic regulations and validations for athletes including Noah Carter, ensuring that their performance results and equipment use comply with set standards.

Overall, the World Athletics Federation plays a pivotal role in maintaining the integrity of international athletics by validating records and enforcing rules and guidelines that ensure fair competition and adherence to established norms. The federation oversees the validation of Noah Carter's new 100m sprint record, as well as his participation and records in the championship. It validates new records set by athletes like Noah Carter who break records at championships and recognizes their achievements. This comprehensive oversight ensures that all aspects of Noah Carter’s athletic performance are validated and recognized according to the highest standards of international athletics.&lt;SEP&gt;The World Athletics Federation oversees the rules and regulations for athletes like Noah Carter competing in the championship.&lt;SEP&gt;The World Athletics Federation oversees the rules and regulations under which Noah Carter competes in international championships.&lt;SEP&gt;The World Athletics Federation oversees and validates records set by athletes like Noah Carter.&lt;SEP&gt;The World Athletics Federation oversees the rules and regulations Noah Carter must follow during competitions.</data>
  <data key="d9">athlete governance,athlete oversight,athlete recognition,athlete regulation,athlete supervision,athletic achievement,competition oversight,governance,governing body,record validation,regulation,validation</data>
