  <data key="d7">17.0</data>
  <data key="d8">(B人員, C客戶) is a relation where B人員 provides various maintenance and technical support services to C 고객. This relationship includes responsibilities such as maintaining C客户的 systems, providing ongoing technical support, and handling related maintenance tasks as documented in the maintenance record. B人员 acts not only as a service provider but also as an engineer who ensures the continuous functionality of C客户的 systems by addressing any technical issues and implementing necessary maintenance procedures. These responsibilities encompass both proactive measures to prevent system failures and reactive actions in response to existing problems, all meticulously recorded for reference and continuity purposes.

B人員 is specifically responsible for performing maintenance services for C客户 during the specified time period and ensuring that all maintenance-related activities are accurately documented and managed. This role also involves B人员 handling the maintenance record of C客戶, which includes on-site service provided as part of the overall maintenance process. B人员 not only conducts maintenance work but also offers engineering support to C客户提供维护支持和工程服务, thereby covering a wide range of technical needs.

Overall, B人員 plays a critical role in maintaining and supporting C客户的 systems through comprehensive maintenance services that include both reactive fixes and proactive measures aimed at preventing system failures.&lt;SEP&gt;B人员负责为客户C客户提供维护服务。&lt;SEP&gt;B人员conducted maintenance work for C客户.</data>
